Two questions:
1. When you say the latest TensorFlow wheel, do you mean `sudo pip install --upgrade https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/linux/cpu/tensorflow-0.8.0-cp27-none-linux_x86_64.whl`, or did you download the nightly build?
2. What was the context for this error? i.e. what did you input to the function?
